name: Noah Garrett
text: Mod has super friendly staff who gave amazing service despite it being crazy busy! I loved the outdoor seating, and the interior was welcoming, aesthetically pleasing, and laid out really well. Oh, and the pizza? To die for. Definitely going to be coming back!

name: Jordan Nelson
text: I have had Mod a few times and on the good to great spectrum, it's been good but far from great. At the new restaurant in Moscow I had my first experience that was much closer to great. Good service, as usual, but the pizza was excellent. Excited to go back.

text: Gotta love the subway of pizza! Quick ordering, cook time, and you still get great taste! Also I like how open the seating is. Doesn't feel cramped like most places in the Moscow area.
